casebody.data:
Dillard L. LANE v. Robert H. HUDSPETH, Warden, United States Penitentiary, Leavenworth, Kan. No. 2032. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Jan. 2, 1940. Edward H. Powers, of Kansas City, Kan., for appellant. Homer Davis, Asst.. U. S. Atty., of Topeka, Kan., for appellee.

Before LEWIS and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on application of appellant.
